theorem Topology.frontier_closed {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    IsClosed (frontier A) := by
  simpa [frontier] using
    (Topology.isClosed_boundary (X := X) (A := A))

theorem Topology.frontier_closure_eq_closure_diff_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    frontier (closure A) = closure A \ interior (closure A) := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    rcases hx with ⟨hxClos, hxNotInt⟩
    -- `closure (closure A)` simplifies to `closure A`
    have hxClos' : x ∈ closure A := by
      simpa [closure_closure] using hxClos
    exact And.intro hxClos' hxNotInt
  · intro hx
    rcases hx with ⟨hxClos, hxNotInt⟩
    -- From `x ∈ closure A`, we obtain `x ∈ closure (closure A)`
    have hxClos' : x ∈ closure (closure A) := by
      simpa [closure_closure] using hxClos
    exact And.intro hxClos' hxNotInt

theorem Topology.interior_closure_subset_closure_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) := by
  intro x hx
  exact (subset_closure : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A))) hx
